Package edu.bonn.cs.wmp.awarenesswidgets

Interface Summary
WMPAwarenessWidget This interface defines all methods necessary for any WMPAwarenessWidget.
 

Class Summary
ContentChange Super class for all types of content changes.
LineChange This content change type shall be used for propagating line lenght changes from a WMPEditText to a RadarView.
RadarView This Awareness Widget shows the complete currently edited document.
ViewportChange This change type is used to tell a RadarView about the new viewport position of a specific user.
